@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<div class="container mt-5">
    <h1 class="mb-4 text-center">About CareSync</h1>
    <p class="lead text-center">
        CareSync helps patients book appointments with healthcare providers by simplifying the search and booking process.
    </p>

    <hr class="my-5" />

    <h2 style="text-align: center;">Our Team</h2>
    <p style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto 30px; font-size: 1.1rem; text-align: center;">
        CareSync application was developed collaboratively by our team of four, with each member contributing to both frontend and backend tasks, including UI design, CRUD implementation, data modeling, and interactive chart integration.
    </p>

    <div class="team-container">
        <div class="team-card">
            <img src="~/images/debjani.jpg" alt="Debjani Sarma" />
            <h4>Debjani Sarma</h4>
            <p>Worked across both frontend and backend layers, focusing on designing the homepage and charts UI using CSS and layout principles. Collaborated on data integration, logical modeling, and dynamic visualization of appointment statistics.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
            <img src="~/images/naveen.jpg" alt="Naveen Pogiri" />
            <h4>Naveen Pogiri</h4>
            <p>Contributed to the full-stack development of the application, including database schema design and implementation of data visualizations using Chart.js. Collaborated on integrating the logical data model and contributed to UI refinement and chart-related logic.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
            <img src="~/images/pratap.jpg" alt="Sai Pratap Kodidasu" />
            <h4>Sai Pratap Kodidasu</h4>
            <p>Led implementation of core CRUD functionalities, appointment scheduling logic, and backend integration. Also contributed to frontend form handling, data flow management, and collaborated on modeling and statistics features.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="team-card">
            <img src="~/images/sharmila.jpg" alt="Divya Sharmila Penumaka" />
            <h4>Divya Sharmila Penumaka</h4>
            <p>
                Co-developed frontend UI components and data binding features. Participated in database design, contact and about page styling, and supported integration of the logical data model with Chart.js for statistical visualization.

            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <hr class="my-5" />

    <h2 class="mb-3">Logical Data Model</h2>
    <img src="~/images/data-model.png" alt="Logical Data Model" class="img-fluid mb-4" style="max-width: 600px;" />

    <h2 class="mt-5">GitHub Repository</h2>
    <p>
        Explore the source code:
        <a href="https://github.com/naveenpogiri11/ADA_CareSync_Project.git" target="_blank">
            GitHub Repository
        </a>
    </p>
</div>
